node.title: Crash on SH20 causing delays near Māngere East
node.description: A crash is blocking one lane on State Highway 20 near Māngere East in Auckland.
node.content:
["A crash is blocking one southbound lane on State Highway 20 near Māngere East in Auckland.", "", "
Southbound traffic on SH20 near Mangere East in Auckland was backed up after a crash on 22 December, 2021. Photo: RNZ / Kymberlee Fernandes
", "NZTA said the crash, which happened after 6pm, was causing delays in the area between Massey Rd and Puhinui Rd."]
